# id: HttpComponentsClientHttpRequest -> static void addHeaders(HttpUriRequest httpRequest, HttpHeaders headers)
commentText: Adds the given headers to the given HTTP request.__@param httpRequest the request to add the headers to_@param headers the headers to add
codeText: static void addHeaders(HttpUriRequest httpRequest, HttpHeaders headers) {_		for (Map.Entry<String, List<String>> entry : headers.entrySet()) {_			String headerName = entry.getKey()__			if (!headerName.equalsIgnoreCase(HTTP.CONTENT_LEN) &&_					!headerName.equalsIgnoreCase(HTTP.TRANSFER_ENCODING)) {_				for (String headerValue : entry.getValue()) {_					httpRequest.addHeader(headerName, headerValue)__				}_			}_		}_	}
